VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT subprocess\.run\(.*\)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(shell=True|input\(|request|params|query|argv) && MISSING:(shlex\.quote|list2cmdline|allowlist|whitelist)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects instances of subprocess.run() that can lead to command injection vulnerabilities if used with untrusted input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Command Injection: subprocess.
